          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>North Korea Ballistic Missile Investigations Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of the Director of National Intelligence to conduct an investigation and report to Congress regarding North Korea's alleged procurement of engines and related technology from foreign sources.</p>]]></text>
